{"tid":926094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★大型玩具店員工爆料：聖誕千祈唔好做 full time $9500","createTime":"2018-12-03T07:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T06:22:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"352533b53d0b522a8073ff93100f2851af308553","tid":926094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"從業員上網大爆料，叫人千祈唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「呢間公司其實真心出名人工低門檻低，好啱返緊學做pt；但問題係佢onX到一定要OTOT，都算，仲要成日有啲19 buyer行場成日嫌三嫌四；自己啲貨垃圾緊係唔會有人買啦﹗第二19就係啲X客啲X客永遠都係最唔夠人嘅時候先攪事，仲要以為自己識投訴好撚勁；OnX仔我話你知，呢間公司你點投訴都唔會攪到我呢啲pt仔，呢間公間長期唔夠人用，人工又低，邊度會留得住人？我係呢度呼籲各位，千祈唔好做﹗」</strong><br />\n<br />\n一問之下，似乎都唔少人做過呢間公司，有網友自爆做一日已經頂唔順即走，有人更踢爆full time 都得9500蚊，聖誕入去隨時「做死人」﹗<br />\n唔好入去做，仲有幾個致命原因：<br />\n<br />\n經理會話你唔夠笑容<br />\n老seafood輕視年輕員工<br />\n神秘顧客玩員工<br />\n已cut聖誕bonus<br />\n客人鼻哥窿向天<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">來源：連登</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%8E%A9%E5%85%B7%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E5%8D%83%E7%A5%88%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%81%9A-031454790.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%2585%25B7%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2599-%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E5%258D%2583%25E7%25A5%2588%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%2581%259A-031454790.html&d=E19L6z%2Bp8GfveTtRqWmKGcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b0dbe01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%8E%A9%E5%85%B7%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E5%8D%83%E7%A5%88%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%81%9A-031454790.html</a>"},{"pid":"f13516a714a7640393c78860d8beb0a0791aad8f","tid":926094,"uid":19454,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/0